videos.description: Jessica Shepard gets the feed and puts her defender in a blender with a spin move for an open jump shot.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Shepard drills turn-around jumper

videos.description: Notre Dame is breaking down the the Florida State defense with impressive passes underneath that lead to layups.
videos.headline: Irish use great passing for easy buckets

videos.description: AJ Alix throws a lob pass over the Notre Dame defense to Ama Degbeon who rises up and hits the layup.
videos.headline: FSU's Alix tosses impressive assist to Degbeon
